title: Will Genia sent for scans on injured knee
text:
Will Genia sent for scans on injured ... Will Genia sent for scans on injured knee Next Story Prev Story 6 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Wallabies halfback Will Genia has been taken for scans on his injured knee and could be ruled out of the squad that will travel to Argentina for the second Test of the Rugby Championship. Genia played only the first half of Australia's dramatic 24-20 comeback win over South Africa on Friday night in Brisbane, having limped off at the break with suspected medial ligament damage.   The Age.
